# Trivy ignore file
# Use this file to suppress findings ONLY after a documented risk acceptance
# has been signed off by the Security Champion + Engineering Manager.
#
# Format:
#   <CVE-ID>      # Reason: <ticket-id> - <short justification> - expires <YYYY-MM-DD>
#
# Example (commented out):
# CVE-2023-99999  # Reason: SEC-1234 - false positive in transitive dep, expires 2026-12-31
